"Vrnite se na ponudbo, ki ste jo ustvarili prej, in kliknite nanjo. "
"'<strong>Potrdite</strong>' gumb. Vaša ponudba je zdaj<strong>Prodajno "
"Naročilo. </strong>"

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to 'Configuration &amp;gt; Worksheet Templates' and click on "
"'<strong>Analysis</strong>' from your '<strong>Worksheet Template</strong>' "
"form view."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na 'Konfiguracijo &amp;gt; Predloge delovnih listov' in kliknite na "
"'<strong>Analizo</strong>' iz vaše '<strong>Predloge delovnega lista</"
"strong>' pogleda obrazca."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to 'Dashboards &amp;gt; Projects' to get an overview of your tasks. <span "
"style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; background-"
"color: inherit;\">Use predefined </span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; "
"background-color: inherit;\"><strong>dashboards</strong></span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-"
"weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\"> or build your own with the "
"advanced reporting engine. Share filters with the team.</span>"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na 'Nadzorne plošče &amp;gt; Projekti' da dobite pregled nad svojimi "
"nalogami. <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-weight: "
"400; background-color: inherit;\">Uporabite vnaprej določene </span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; "
"background-color: inherit;\"><strong>nadzorne plošče </strong></span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-"
"weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\"> ali pa si ustvarite svojega z "
"naprednim mehanizmom za poročanje. Delite filtre z ekipo.</span>"

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to Reporting &amp;gt; <strong>Tasks Analysis</strong> to get statistics "
"on your tasks and to analyze the performance of your projects."
msgstr ""
"Pojdi na Poročanje &amp;gt; <strong>Analiza nalog </strong> za pridobitev "
"statističnih podatkov o vaših nalogah in za analizo uspešnosti vaših "
"projektov."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to the 'Configuration &amp;gt; Stages' menu. Then define a "
"'<strong>Rating Email Template</strong>' on your 'Done' stage (or any other "
"one you'd like). This will automatically send a <strong>rating request</"
"strong> to the\n"
"                    customer once the task reaches this stage."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v meni »Konfiguracija in faze«. Nato definirajte '<strong>Predlogo e-"
"poštnega sporočila z oceno\n"
"</strong>' na stopnji »Končano« (ali kateri koli drugi, ki jo želite). To bo "
"samodejno poslalo <strong>zahteva za oceno</strong> stranki,\n"
"                    ko naloga doseže to fazo."

